  "prompt": "Are there any hotels in Goa which could be safe for unmarried couples?",
  "response": "Yes, there are many hotels in Goa that are safe for unmarried couples. Modern hotels and resorts generally have progressive policies and prioritize the privacy and comfort of their guests. Some popular hotels in Goa that are known to be couple-friendly include:\n\n1. **Taj Exotica Resort & Spa** - A luxury hotel that offers exceptional service and privacy.\n2. **The Leela Goa** - Renowned for its stunning location and couple-friendly environment.\n3. **Novotel Goa Resort and Spa** - Provides comfortable accommodations and a safe atmosphere for all guests.\n4. **Park Hyatt Goa Resort and Spa** - Known for its beautiful surroundings and excellent service.\n5. **W Goa** - A trendy and luxurious hotel ideal for couples seeking a relaxing getaway.\n6. **Vivanta Goa** - A part of the prestigious Taj group, ensuring quality and privacy.\n7. **Treebo Hotels** - An affordable option with several properties in Goa that welcome unmarried couples.\n\nWhen booking, it's advised to verify the hotel's policy regarding unmarried couples, which can usually be done by checking their website or directly contacting the hotel. Carrying valid identification and being respectful of local norms can ensure a hassle-free stay.",
